  "title": "Retail Assistant (Full-Time / Part-Time)",
  "description": "<h2><strong>✨ Retail Assistant (Full-Time / Part-Time) ✨</strong></h2><h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><p>Join our team and grow with us! We are looking for friendly, motivated individuals to work as <strong>Retail Assistants</strong> in a fun and supportive retail environment. Both <strong>full-time and part-time</strong> applicants are welcome.</p><h3><strong>📍 Work Locations</strong></h3><p>• Ang Mo Kio (AMK)<br />• Farrer Park – City Square Mall<br />• Bedok</p><h3><strong>💼 Job Responsibilities</strong></h3><p>• Assist customers with enquiries and purchases<br />• Maintain cleanliness and organisation of the store<br />• Replenish stock and manage inventory<br />• Operate cashier and handle payment transactions<br />• Support overall store operations and other assigned duties</p><h3><strong>🎁 Benefits</strong></h3><p>• Medical benefits<br />• Annual leave entitlement<br />• Annual company trip<br />• Shop incentive schemes</p><h3><strong>🕒 Working Hours & Pay Structure</strong></h3><p><strong>Full-Time Positions</strong></p><p><strong>AMK & City Square Mall Branches</strong><br />• <strong>5-Day Work Week:</strong><br />  1 weekday off + 1 weekend day off<br />  11:00 AM – 9:00 PM (2-hour break)<br />• <strong>6-Day Work Week:</strong><br />  Choose 1 day off<br />  11:00 AM – 9:00 PM (2-hour break)</p><p><strong>Bedok Branch</strong><br />• <strong>5-Day Work Week:</strong><br />  1 weekday off + 1 weekend day off<br />  8:30 AM – 5:30 PM (1-hour break)<br />• <strong>6-Day Work Week:</strong><br />  Choose 1 day off<br />  8:30 AM – 5:30 PM (1-hour break)</p><p><strong>Part-Time Positions</strong></p><p>• $10/hour<br />• $12/hour on Public Holidays<br />• Minimum commitment: <strong>3 days per week</strong></p><h3><strong>📌 Reporting Officer</strong></h3><p>Retail Supervisor</p><h3><strong>📩 How to Apply</strong></h3><p>Interested applicants, please submit your resume/CV to:<br />📧 <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">hr@uonegolive.com</a></p>",
